<% layout('../layouts/base') %>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tajawal:wght@300&display=swap');
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Questrial&display=swap');
        main {
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        .adoption_container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .adoption_ways .heading {
            font-family: 'Questrial', sans-serif;   
            display: grid;
            grid-template-rows: 1fr;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .adoption_ways .heading h1 {
            font-size: 70px;
            color: #2356A9;
        }
        .adoption_ways .cards {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
        }
        .adoption_ways .cards .first_row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            margin: 50px;
        }
        .adoption_ways .cards .card {
            box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35) 0px 5px 15px;
            display: grid;
            justify-items: center;
            background-color: white;
            margin: 10px;
            height: 280px !important;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }
        .adoption_ways button {
            color: white;
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-left: 10px;
            height: 40px;
            width: 300px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 15px;
            background-color: #FD9789;
        }
        .adoption_ways h2 {
            font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif;
            color: #2356A9;
        }
        .adoption_ways p {
            font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif;
            text-justify: auto;
            color: gray;
        }
        .adoption_ways a {
            color: white;
        }
        .container_five {
            padding-left: 100px;
        }
    </style>
    <main>
        <div class="mycontainer">
            <div class="container-one">
                <div class="inner-container">
                    <div class="des-box-left" data-aos="fade-right">
                        <h1></span>Adopting a pet has never been easier</h1>
                        <p>Pet adoption can be a rewarding and fulfilling experience for both the pet and the owner.
                            However, it can also be a daunting task, especially for first-time pet owners. Fortunately,
                            we are here for the rescue. Our website helps you to find your pet partner and add more joy
                            to your life.
                            We promote adopting rescued pets from shelter rather than purchasing from breeders.
                            <br> <br>We wish you a joyful journey exploring pets on our website and be their forever
                            family.
                        </p>
                        <div class="buttons">
                            <button class="find-pet"><a href="/NewMembers" style="color: white">Find Pets</a></button>
                            <button class="sign-up"><a href="/signup" style="color: #2356A9">Sign Up</a></button>
                        </div>
                    </div>


                    <div class="img-box-right" data-aos="fade-left">
                        <img src="/img/Dog1.png" alt="dog" height="500px" width="500px" style="box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35) 0px 5px 15px; border-radius: 24px" >
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="container-two">
                <div class="main-container">
                    <div class="title">
                        <img src="/img/paws.png" alt="paws" />
                        <h2>Why You Should Adopt?</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cards-container">
                        <div class="card card-one" style="box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35) 0px 5px 15px;" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-duration="1500">
                            <h1>1</h1>
                            <p>If more people adopted pets instead of buying them, the number of pets euthanized would
                                lower dramatically.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card card-two" style="box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35) 0px 5px 15px;" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-duration="1500">
                            <h1>2</h1>
                            <p>You not only do you save your loving new companion, but you make space for other animals
                                who need it.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card card-three" style="box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35) 0px 5px 15px;" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-duration="1500">
                            <h1>3</h1>
                            <p>Factory-style breeding facilities that often prioritize profit over animal welfare.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div> 





            <div class="adoption_container">
                <div class="adoption_ways">
                    <div class="heading">
                        <div><hr></div>
                        <div><h1>Other ways to adopt a Pet</h1></div>
                        <div><hr></div>
                    </div>
                    <br><br>
                    <div class="cards">
                        <div class="first_row">
                            <div class="trial_adoption card" data-aos-duration="1500" data-aos="fade-right">
                                <h2>TRIAL ADOPTION</h2>
                                <p>Our Foster to Family program is a great opportunity to bring a pet home for 2 weeks for a trial adoption. You'll even get full support from our foster team for those 2 weeks. This allows you time to ensure the pet's a great fit for your family!
                                </p>
                                <a href="/trial"><button>LEARN MORE</button></a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="foster_pets card" data-aos-duration="1500" data-aos="fade-left">
                                <h2>FOSTER PETS</h2>
                                <p>Avoid the shelter and browse our pets available for adoption who are living in foster homes with a foster family. Foster parents can provide great information about their foster pet to you.</p>
                                <a href="/foster"><button>LEARN MORE</button></a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="first_row">
                            <div class="trial_adoption card" data-aos="fade-right">
                                <h2>FAMILY-TO-FAMILY</h2>
                                <p>Sometimes, situations change and loved pets need to find new homes. You can adopt a pet directly from their current guardians, preventing them from ever spending a night in an animal shelter!</p>
                                <a href="/family"><button>LEARN MORE</button></a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="foster_pets card" data-aos="fade-left">
                                <h2>PETS FOR PATRIOTS</h2>
                                <p>LifeLine supports military veterans by partnering with Pets for Patriots to help them adopt a new best friend for free. Every Pets for Patriots member receives discounts on vet care, pet food, treats, medication and so much more!
                                </p>
                                <a href="https://www.petsforpatriots.org/adopt-a-pet/how-it-works/"><button>LEARN MORE</button></a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
